        <section>
            <h2>About Peruvanthanam</h2>
            <p>Peruvanthanam, a tranquil village in Idukki, Kerala, is a serene escape nestled amidst lush hills and forests, offering a blend of natural beauty and cultural heritage, perfect for a rejuvenating getaway. 
                The village is surrounded by hills, forests, and rivers, making it an ideal destination for nature lovers. 
      The is home to ancient temples and churches, reflecting its diverse and vibrant history. 
        </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Image at the center -->
